For example [this code](https://github.com/mono/SkiaSharp/blob/master/samples/Skia.WindowsDesktop.Demo/SkiaView.cs#L29) can be now simplified as:

``` csharp
        protected override void OnPaint(PaintEventArgs e)
        {
            if (onDrawCallback == null)
                return;
            using (var ctx = _renderTarget.CreateRenderContext())
                onDrawCallback(ctx.Canvas, Width, Height);
        }

```
